{"tid":2278542,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼滅之刃為何大紅？他舉人氣角色「我妻善逸」分析：讀者有共鳴","createTime":"2020-11-09T08:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T16:57:41.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3aeb5ac8320cda440f9642df6e6b2ff40ad48636","tid":2278542,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:31:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/11/07/1/9031379.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=465&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F11%2F07%2F1%2F9031379.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D465%26nt%3D1&h=342ca34f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人氣動漫「鬼滅之刃」電影動畫「無限列車篇」人氣持續高漲，日本票房目前已經突破200億日幣大關，台灣上映後同樣已經超過2.5億台幣。就有日本媒體以劇中的人氣角色，分析作品大紅的魅力在哪。<br />\n<br />\n根據日本媒體「文春Online」報導，連載鬼滅之刃的漫畫雜誌「少年週刊JUMP」，在10月26日公布了鬼滅之刃的人氣角色投票。而拿下人氣王的角色，並不是主角竈門炭治郎，反而是另一位配角「我妻善逸」。<br />\n<br />\n報導分析，作品中與鬼對抗的「鬼殺隊」，成員大多有著置生死於度外的性格。唯獨我妻善逸，經常把「好痛」、「不想死啊」等台詞掛在嘴邊，誠實面對自己弱小的一面，反而塑造出親近感。<br />\n<br />\n而隨著劇情進展，我妻善逸還會在極端狀況下爆發出強大實力，以及故事中後段的成長，又更爭取了讀者認同。此外，我妻善逸雖然有著整天想吃女生豆腐，帶有花心男的形象，但他卻常在關鍵之中，出手保護女主角禰豆子，因此能博得女性讀者的肯定。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/11/01/realtime/8945611.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=400&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F11%2F01%2Frealtime%2F8945611.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D400%26nt%3D1&h=d7c1bb8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此外在反派陣營，如黒死牟、猗窩座等角色在投票中，也具有一定的人氣。這是因為作品在描寫這些反派時，也強調他們從人類變成鬼的悲慘過程，不單單只是把他們寫成壞人。如此複雜的情感，反而能加深讀者的印象。<br />\n<br />\n報導認為，正是在描寫人物上極為出色，因此不分性別立場的讀者，總會在故事中找到能產生共鳴的角色，才讓鬼滅之刃如此受到歡迎。"},{"pid":"1f1fc56513883a68c4047f00c0a719d7bfd34d6e","tid":2278542,"uid":147292,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:37:48.000Z","msg":"善逸同班毒撚一樣廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔同嘅係 善逸危急關頭會爆發潛能，但毒撚冇潛能<br />\n整個角色俾毒撚代入ff下，咪多人鐘意"},{"pid":"d0caa1ae3cbe1b96d631c459b6ecad37c39ef8e6","tid":2278542,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":39,"score":-38,"quote":{"pid":"1f1fc56513883a68c4047f00c0a719d7bfd34d6e","tid":2278542,"uid":147292,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:37:48.000Z","msg":"善逸同班毒撚一樣廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔同嘅係 善逸危急關頭會爆發潛能，但毒撚冇潛能<br />\n整個角色俾毒撚代入ff下，咪多人鐘意"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:59:44.000Z","msg":"唔係喎<br />\n蛙妹都好中意善逸<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FNta4KWTyYc&amp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFNta4KWTyYc%26&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=95b9798b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FNta4KWTyYc&amp;</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3A8FmAaybps\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3A8FmAaybps&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=5bd70ded\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3A8FmAaybps</a>"},{"pid":"1c6950a3594bd82cbd1460e041fa397f19279f52","tid":2278542,"uid":26109,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"d0caa1ae3cbe1b96d631c459b6ecad37c39ef8e6","tid":2278542,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":39,"score":-38,"quote":{"pid":"1f1fc56513883a68c4047f00c0a719d7bfd34d6e","tid":2278542,"uid":147292,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:37:48.000Z","msg":"善逸同班毒撚一樣廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔同嘅係 善逸危急關頭會爆發潛能，但毒撚冇潛能<br />\n整個角色俾毒撚代入ff下，咪多人鐘意"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:59:44.000Z","msg":"唔係喎<br />\n蛙妹都好中意善逸<br />\n<a href=\"ht